\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt 1 Samuel 2:9; Onger Akaba 66:9\x*God gumazamizibar gari, me gumazamizir igharaziba deragha arazir magh gariba me gami, ezÉØ a deravÉØra men gara men akura. 
